// Held-out routing eval (English) for the FunctionGemma promotion gate.
//
// EVERY case here is a keyword-MISS. The router is the FALLBACK tier: it only
// runs when the keyword scorer finds nothing, so a case the keyword scorer
// already wins never reaches the router in production and scoring the router
// on it measures nothing. `route-eval` enforces this (exits 3 on a polluted
// eval) — verified against `Engine::keyword_decision` under locale "en".
//
// NONE = the router must abstain (general knowledge → assistant). Positives
// are canonical English skill requests the keyword tier misses and a competent
// router must still route — oblique phrasings, not tricks.
//
// Every utterance is also HELD OUT: absent from generate-dataset.py's English
// training corpus (builtin *_EXAMPLES_EN, community SKILL.en.md examples, and
// the English negative pool), compared on the normalised form. A pass means
// the model GENERALISED, not memorised.
//
// Note: "search" is keyword-only (router_eligible=false), so it is never a
// positive target here.
{"utterance": "what is the capital of Denmark", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "who painted Starry Night", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "how tall is Mount Kilimanjaro", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "who discovered penicillin", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what is the largest planet in the solar system", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what is the boiling point of nitrogen", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what year was the Magna Carta signed", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "how many legs does a spider have", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what is the chemical formula for water", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what causes a rainbow", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "how do magnets work", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what is the deepest lake in the world", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "who wrote Pride and Prejudice", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what is the speed of sound", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "how far is Mars from the sun", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what is the smallest bone in the human body", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "who founded Microsoft", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what is the national animal of Scotland", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "how many keys are on a piano", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what is the hardest natural material", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "who was the first emperor of Rome", "expect": "NONE"}
{"utterance": "what does photosynthesis produce", "expect": "NONE"}
